race.comment: Loads of win chances. IMPONDERABLE (13) showed plenty of ability on debut then didn't go a yard in the very heavy ground last time. Back on firmer footing this time and the trip suits and is drawn for the run of the race just off the pace. Expected to bounce. VERY FAMOUS (14) hasn't been far away at all three runs to date. Making progress and among the main hopes. HABITUAL (5) is worth another try. Solid run way out of his class last time and deserves another chance back in a maiden. AGGRESSIVE (9) finished off last campaign in stakes class. Resuming at home with the blinkers on and expected to feature.
